                        <div class="faq-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>To connect to a new database, navigate to the Database Connector page and click "Add New Connection". Fill in your database credentials including host, port, database name, username, and password. Test the connection before saving.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <h4>What file formats are supported for data import?</h4>
                        <div class="faq-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                        </div>
